- To compile the codes, you need to set the path to halide root directory.
- The scripts ./demo_live.sh, ./demo_gpu.sh and ./demo_cori.sh should compile
the codes and run the demo program with the appropriate input data.

Running on NERSC
----------------
- To compile and run on NERSC Edison, you need to execute "source
  env-edison.sh" first.

- The "run-edison.sbatch" Slurm script should be edited during demo time to
  have the correct account number (-A option) and reservation name
  (--reservation option).

